                            <comment id="17781533" author="benedict" created="Tue, 31 Oct 2023 21:51:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the report. Counter columns are inherently not transactional, and I don&apos;t know why they are permitted to be included in transactions. I assume it&apos;s an oversight. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=maedhroz&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;maedhroz&quot;&gt;maedhroz&lt;/a&gt; can you take a look?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
